AB  - Background: The stigma attached to mental disorders has been recognized as a major concern in healthcare services across societies.
   Aims: To compare the stigmatizing attitude towards patients with schizophrenia between the general public, relatives of patient with schizophrenia and relatives of patient with neurotic illnesses.
